###############################################################################
Raspberry PI as a home theatre player
###############################################################################

Basic setup
===========
Hardware: Raspberry Pi
Software: Pi OS, Apache2 webserver, omxplayer
App: CGI script written in Bash

web client --- CGI script on Pi --- omxplayer on Pi 

Steps
=========

on pi:
run pi_setup.sh 
set passwordless login from smstong@cf-31 to pi and root.

on cf-31:
run pi_install.sh
